title: Srrauss, R. - Also sprah Zarathustra - Previn, VPO
description:
Richard Strauss: Also sprach Zarathustra, Tod und Verlarung.

Richard Strauss' Also sprach Zarathustra, op. 30 and Tod und Verklarung, op. 24, recorded by the Vienna Philharmonic Orchestra, conducted by Andre Previn. This CD was released by Telarc in 1988. Even if the only version you love is Karajan's, you have to hear this one!

Please enjoy.
